lient", "recommendations/3/date": "January 30, 2017", "recommendations/3/description": "Worked with Matt for several years when he contracted Thailand. Matt was highly professional, a good negotiator who always looked for a win win. Great follow up and always reliable. ", "recommendations/3/name": "Matthew Bramich", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Product, Purchasing & Operations Director Inghams & Santas Lapland", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthew-bramich-4558963a/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhRRAEBSJXnEuyiARx0uGUPnDTXpz5NxG8", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Viktor worked with John but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "October 20, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "John is a highly respected hotel management professional and it is always a pleasure working with him on various initiatives. We have jointly worked on various sales/marketing campaigns and were able to achieve great success in various markets including Canada, USA, Russia/CIS and China. John is a very driven, strategic thinker with extensive sales/marketing background and one of the leaders in Asian hospitality industry. I look forward to working closely with John on many other occasions.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Viktor Spysak", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Global Sales at Air Canada", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vspysak/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABTL1G4B79DKIj0Z7BXByAKtRUe4iUEnh9o", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Sherly worked with John but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "September 22, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "John is really passionate with what he does. Always professional and prompt with his responses. It's been an absolute pleasure working with you in various projects over the years, John. Wishing you the very best in your next step. ",